Start DB
$ sudo mongod

CHECK DB
$ mongo --shell

In mongo shell
1. > db  = show what database are currently using
2. > use activityAnalyzerDB = switch database but if you do not have that it will create new database
3. insert data into database; set up data like Javascript
    3.1 create set of data
               surada = {"name" : "Kalie",
               "position" : "Student",
               "date" : new Data()} Enter!
    3.2 insert data to table
                db.databasename.insert(objectname)

    3.3 show database schema
                db.databasename.find()
                db.databasename.find().pretty() >> to set layout
    3.4 add attribute type array
                objectname.arrayname = []
    3.5 update data (can update more than 1)
                db.databasename.update({"name" : "Surada", objectname)
    3.6 remove object
                db.databasename.remove({"name" : "surada"}) //remove obj which has name "Surada"
    3.7 help
    3.8 exit

Import Json file
mongoimport --db activityAnalyzerDB --collection
sensors --file /DemoDataManager/DataCollected/SensorDataJson/Accelerometer/1506055760997.json --jsonArray
